{"tid":2128395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行會召集人陳智思遭美資銀行取消戶口","createTime":"2020-07-28T03:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T04:17:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51c44b06ba8c130df99cab618d0cc8d9fa5f8c6d","tid":2128395,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:04:00.000Z","msg":"行政會議召集人陳智思表示，他在一間美資銀行的帳戶被關閉，並退回存款，但拒絕透露是哪一間銀行，又指在港區國安法公布後，有關情況愈來愈普遍，相信不少香港政府的高層官員亦面對相同情況。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思在接受《金融時報》訪問時表示，中美關係困擾銀行，美國的銀行，甚至是匯豐銀行，都不願與政治人物有往來，相信除了政府官員，不少民主派人士都會成為被拒絕的客戶名單之一。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思認為關閉銀行帳戶不會危害國家安全，除非有證據證明是受到美國政府指示，以便向香港政府施壓。 <br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行、花旗銀行拒絕就報道置評，同樣在香港有業務的渣打銀行未有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2349301&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBl%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=1c642924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349301</a>"},{"pid":"7c27309d5fbcec09728ff8ab530527f372f5eb72","tid":2128395,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08950e206499aa18d9aff39e4a786fea9e052c74","tid":2128395,"uid":3553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"退回？唔係凍結？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd756e5aa8dcb4bbd3b6bcdc3234320f6aab726","tid":2128395,"uid":130042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"唔用盤谷銀行？唔係佢家族開嘅咩？"},{"pid":"771969715b0ab21eb7522794dfccfd37015ff422","tid":2128395,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"1個是不夠的<br />\n應該全部都要取消"},{"pid":"fa08d5d5d8fbf6218d2ae75cd60879672cbec555","tid":2128395,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfd756e5aa8dcb4bbd3b6bcdc3234320f6aab726",